project.name: Target - advanced
project.notes: How to play: When you click the green flag, the target (the basket) will move to a random spot. Drag the ball to where you want to shoot from, then let go. The ball will move from where you let go, through the X. Then it will continue past the X (while being pulled down by gravity). The farther you are from the release point, the faster the ball will go (and the less it will be pulled down by gravity). The farther down you are, the steeper the angle will be (and the more gravity will be necessary to pull the ball down). You score if you hit the target (the basket). Click the green button again to have the target move to a new random location. You can use the slider to adjust how strong gravity is.
